{"tid":855233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【野豬咬人】野豬闖富山邨咬傷3人 女傷者：好似個人咁大隻！","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T15:24:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"41f80af8e65c2c6b13d51eb21de514908563d7d4","tid":855233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"【野豬咬人】野豬闖富山邨咬傷3人 女傷者：好似個人咁大隻！<br />\n<br />\n1小時前<br />\n即時突發<br />\n <br />\n黃大仙有野豬出沒傷人。早上6時52分，富山邨富信樓地下公廁對開，65歲姓陳女保安員放工後，行至在公廁外遭一頭約300磅重、有獠牙的野豬襲擊，推跌後咬傷她的右腳。陳高聲呼救，驚動一名男街坊，協助雨傘驅趕，但也將他撞傷。<br />\n<br />\n野豬其後跑到附近100米瓊山苑，再襲擊姓陳(79歲)老翁，他遭撞跌頭撼地受傷，野豬又咬他右小腿，剛巧胡志健區議員在場，協助驅趕及報警；野豬傷人後往山上逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場替陳婦及陳伯包紮，協助驅趕的男街坊在現場敷治後拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n陳婦憶述事件時仍然驚魂未定，自言當黑：「好驚呀！好大隻呀！好似個人咁大隻呀！佢撞我囉，避唔到呀，一撞就跌低呀！」她指野豬突然跑出，「(野豬)有牙的。我想去廁所，撞跌之後咬我。我嗌，有個阿伯用遮篤佢。但佢(野豬)唔聽，一路係咁撞，阿伯條褲都爛咗。好驚呀！右腳最傷。」<br />\n警員到場搜捕野豬，暫時沒有發現。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539131248_1641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539131248_1641.jpg&h=89920296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件中兩名傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用雨傘協助驅趕野豬的男子(左二)腳部輕傷。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539131110_81fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539131110_81fb.jpg&h=58d36dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公廁門外遺下大灘血迹。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受傷老婦送院。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受傷老翁送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539132569_aa78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539132569_aa78.jpg&h=0217c3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n區議員胡志健展示傷者揮舞的木棍。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n【野豬咬人】老街坊從未見野豬入邨"},{"pid":"88a2cf22b90506cfb4d06d3457de37bf23f7f0ff","tid":855233,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"個pat 血點解有渣"},{"pid":"8e6f73ee49eb58d6518d8e9fe31624aabb41a383","tid":855233,"uid":128600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88a2cf22b90506cfb4d06d3457de37bf23f7f0ff","tid":855233,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"個pat 血點解有渣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"人血定豬紅？"},{"pid":"9de831bd0cabff7a6e7f2b40cb9f922db84fc315","tid":855233,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e6f73ee49eb58d6518d8e9fe31624aabb41a383","tid":855233,"uid":128600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88a2cf22b90506cfb4d06d3457de37bf23f7f0ff","tid":855233,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"個pat 血點解有渣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"人血定豬紅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"屎黎"},{"pid":"44153ee323788f033d2fad62085c1bb440870c5f","tid":855233,"uid":192189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"隻豬賴屎啊"},{"pid":"0ee440d41d95bd356c8a41dc660ce26ab0d7e9b0","tid":855233,"uid":182758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"野豬都驚"},{"pid":"92bd6f0f527b5e685b4d6dad3e1b7ccc5aaeab4a","tid":855233,"uid":166943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.cinezen.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/20140811-%E8%AC%9D%E4%B8%B9-%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A%E5%B0%8D%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%B9%8B%E5%AD%90_p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinezen.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F08%2F20140811-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E4%25B8%25B9-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E